Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.91,0:01:19.61,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}知晓你的强大的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.97,0:01:25.39,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}人的希望  无名之人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.19,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}赞颂你的内心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.46,0:01:36.05,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}淡淡的小花们
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.38,0:01:41.19,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}坚韧不挠的藤蔓的形状
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.85,0:01:46.61,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}怀中藏有刺的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.08,0:01:53.59,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}各自怀着不可言喻的昨天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.34,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}向天空而去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.74,0:02:02.80,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}只要生命还在  就喊出愿望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.11,0:02:08.30,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}心意终将贯穿星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.52,0:02:13.59,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}在漫长又短暂的时间的尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.14,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}你生存过的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.14,0:02:18.04,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}证据会
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.02,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}顶起土壤
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.68,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}明日发芽
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.68,0:02:27.99,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}终将绽放大朵鲜花
